router

### Description

Right now there is no way to get all params from nested snapshots. One has to loop through snapshot.children to get all params. 

### Proposed solution

Either something like `paramsInheritanceStrategy: 'always',`

Or 

`activatedRoute.getAllParams()`

### Alternatives considered

Following functions compiles all params but its un-necessary and I feel framework should provide this out of the box

```
getAllParams = () =>{
        let snapshot = this.activatedRoute.snapshot;
        while(snapshot.children.length > 0){
            snapshot = snapshot.children[0];
        }
        return snapshot.params;
    }
```

